text: Sofia Church () is a church in the town of Jönköping in Sweden. It belongs to Sofia-Järstorp Parish of the Church of Sweden. It was opened on 8 April 1888. That day was the Octave of Easter. == References == ==Other websites== Category:Church of Sweden churches Category:Buildings and structures in Jönköping Category:Buildings and structures completed in the 19th century
